    "name": "Mage Food Truck",
    "steam_appid": 3043320,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A roguelike culinary fantasy adventure! Use your growing card collection to explore a hangry realm, crafting exotic ingredients into delicious dishes. Can you score enough gold for a rave review, or will your crew be undone by fantastical beasts and curses from dissatisfied customers? Runs take about 45 minutes.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each run consists of a Morning, Day, and Night shift, with turn events that become increasingly perilous. You'll play hands from your growing card collection to traverse the realm, collect ingredients, craft recipes, and  earn as much gold as possible. When the day is done or your truck is wrecked by monsters, your customers shall pass judgment upon you with a review of 0-3 stars! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each work day begins with a small starter deck, and you’ll purchase new cards from the Turvy Mart at the end of each turn. Play a Job card to use any crew member's ability, which you can combine with other cards from your hand to boost productivity! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043320/extras/918e2924891264d8d5fd3d14565a110a.avif?t=1769091763\" width=612 height=268 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Explorer</strong> travels around the map, seeking ingredients and delivering food</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Chef</strong> crafts recipes with ingredients you've collected</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Mage</strong> protects your truck with a magic shield and fights off pesky curses</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Bard</strong> motivates your crew with EXP, unlocking powerful Special cards unique to each crew member</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043320/extras/3bc0900dd50e620e2393f558eb484b9a.avif?t=1769091763\" width=616 height=272 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 Tutorial Scenarios &amp; 2 Replayable Scenarios: Ease into the mechanics or dive in head first!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customizable difficulty: Add some spice in the Scoville menu to gain a score multiplier</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >15+ ingredients make over 25 delicious illustrated recipes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >40+ Unique events to bless or curse your truck</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Score Attack: Craft and deliver as much food as possible before your work day is over</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock the favor of mighty Delectabus, God of Food Trucks</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Optional Vegetarian Mode: Eliminate meat &amp; gain some unique recipes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Controllers supported!</p></li></ul>",
